question: How many people lived in Odense Municipality, Denmark on July 1, 2022?
asked_question_translated: Hvor mange mennesker boede der i Odense Kommune, Danmark, den 1. juli 2022?
answer: Den 1. juli 2022 boede der cirka 206.305 mennesker i Odense Kommune, Danmark.
answer_translated_eng: On 1 July 2022 there were approximately 206,305 people living in Odense Municipality, Denmark.
